<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="115">
Head and mesosoma dark reddish brown (Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figures 1–6" captionStartId="F1" captionText="Figures 1 - 6. Probles arkadyi sp. nov., holotype, female 1 habitus, lateral view 2 antennae, dorso-lateral view 3 head, front view 4 head, ventral view 5 head and mesoscutum, dorsal view 6 head and mesosoma, lateral view." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.84.68719.figures1-6" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/579261" pageId="0" pageNumber="115">6</figureCitation>
